column5: Hey there Hombres,  I'm on a job site north of Latchford and I should be done early, around 1:30-2. If you want to meet up to fish for SMB and pike on some easy access lakes shoot me a PM. Gotta love using a phone as a modem. I'm looking at trying either James or Granite Lk.
a little far but next time you are in or around sault ste. marie or st. joe's, let me know in advance and we'll "hook up".
It's only a few hundred Kms as the crow flies.....  I'll be taking my last trip to St Joe next week, I'll let you know what day.
No takers? Oh well looks like rocks as ballast will be my fishin partner. Love these work hours!
